---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 61
By: Sri Chandrasekhara Bhâratî Swâmigal
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=God’s Justice
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Concerning Right Vocation or
    ‘Dharma'
---
The place where Dharma and Adharma are done is one. The place where their
fruits are experienced, Heaven or Hell, is elsewhere.
